{"id":50,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":50,"title":"D&C 46","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 46"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to the Church, at Kirtland, Ohio, March 8, 1831. In this early time of the Church, a unified pattern for the conducting of Church services had not yet developed. However, a custom of admitting only members and earnest investigators to the sacrament meetings and other assemblies of the Church had become somewhat general. This revelation expresses the will of the Lord relative to governing and conducting meetings and His direction on seeking and discerning the gifts of the Spirit."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.1-2"},"1–2"],", Elders are to conduct meetings as guided by the Holy Spirit;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.3-6"},"3–6"],", Truth seekers should not be excluded from sacramental services;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7-12"},"7–12"],", Ask of God and seek the gifts of the Spirit;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.13-26"},"13–26"],", An enumeration of some of these gifts is given;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.27-33"},"27–33"],", Church leaders are given power to discern the gifts of the Spirit."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.1","order":"06.05.046.5865"},["b","1"],"Hearken, O ye people of my church; for verily I say unto you that these things were spoken unto you for your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"profit"],"and learning."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.2","order":"06.05.046.5866"},["b","2"],"But notwithstanding those things which are written, it always has been given to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"elders"],"of my church from the beginning, and ever shall be, to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"conduct"],"all meetings as they are directed and guided by the Holy Spirit."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.3","order":"06.05.046.5867"},["b","3"],"Nevertheless ye are commanded never to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"cast"],"any one out from your public",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"meetings"],", which are held before the world."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.4","order":"06.05.046.5868"},["b","4"],"Ye are also commanded not to cast any one who belongeth to the church out of your sacrament meetings; nevertheless, if any have trespassed, let him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"not"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"partake"],"until he makes reconciliation."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.5","order":"06.05.046.5869"},["b","5"],"And again I say unto you, ye shall not cast any out of your sacrament meetings who are earnestly",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"seeking"],"the kingdom—I speak this concerning those who are not of the church."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.6","order":"06.05.046.5870"},["b","6"],"And again I say unto you, concerning your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"confirmation meetings"],", that if there be any that are not of the church, that are earnestly seeking after the kingdom, ye shall not cast them out."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7","order":"06.05.046.5871"},["b","7"],"But ye are commanded in all things to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"ask"],"of God, who giveth liberally; and that which the Spirit testifies unto you even so I would that ye should do in all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"holiness"],"of heart, walking uprightly before me,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"considering"],"the end of your salvation, doing all things with prayer and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"thanksgiving"],", that ye may not be",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"seduced"],"by evil",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_7f"},"spirits"],", or doctrines of devils, or the",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_7g"},"commandments"],"of men; for some are of men, and others of devils."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.8","order":"06.05.046.5872"},["b","8"],"Wherefore, beware lest ye are deceived; and that ye may not be deceived",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"seek"],"ye earnestly the best gifts, always remembering for what they are given;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.9","order":"06.05.046.5873"},["b","9"],"For verily I say unto you, they are given for the benefit of those who love me and keep all my commandments, and him that seeketh so to do; that all may be benefited that seek or that ask of me, that ask and not for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sign"],"that they may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"consume"],"it upon their lusts."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.10","order":"06.05.046.5874"},["b","10"],"And again, verily I say unto you, I would that ye should always remember, and always retain in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"minds"],"what those",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"gifts"],"are, that are given unto the church."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.11","order":"06.05.046.5875"},["b","11"],"For all have not every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"gift"],"given unto them; for there are many gifts, and to every man is given a gift by the Spirit of God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.12","order":"06.05.046.5876"},["b","12"],"To some is given one, and to some is given another, that all may be profited thereby."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.13","order":"06.05.046.5877"},["b","13"],"To some it is given by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Holy Ghost"],"to know that Jesus Christ is the Son of God, and that he was crucified for the sins of the world."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.14","order":"06.05.046.5878"},["b","14"],"To others it is given to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"believe"],"on their words, that they also might have eternal life if they continue faithful."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.15","order":"06.05.046.5879"},["b","15"],"And again, to some it is given by the Holy Ghost to know the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"differences"],"of administration, as it will be pleasing unto the same Lord, according as the Lord will, suiting his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"mercies"],"according to the conditions of the children of men."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.16","order":"06.05.046.5880"},["b","16"],"And again, it is given by the Holy Ghost to some to know the diversities of operations, whether they be of God, that the manifestations of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Spirit"],"may be given to every man to profit withal."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.17","order":"06.05.046.5881"},["b","17"],"And again, verily I say unto you, to some is given, by the Spirit of God, the word of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.18","order":"06.05.046.5882"},["b","18"],"To another is given the word of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"knowledge"],", that all may be taught to be wise and to have knowledge."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.19","order":"06.05.046.5883"},["b","19"],"And again, to some it is given to have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"faith"],"to be healed;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.20","order":"06.05.046.5884"},["b","20"],"And to others it is given to have faith to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.21","order":"06.05.046.5885"},["b","21"],"And again, to some is given the working of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"miracles"],";"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.22","order":"06.05.046.5886"},["b","22"],"And to others it is given to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prophesy"],";"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.23","order":"06.05.046.5887"},["b","23"],"And to others the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"discerning"],"of spirits."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.24","order":"06.05.046.5888"},["b","24"],"And again, it is given to some to speak with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"tongues"],";"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.25","order":"06.05.046.5889"},["b","25"],"And to another is given the interpretation of tongues."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.26","order":"06.05.046.5890"},["b","26"],"And all these",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"gifts"],"come from God, for the benefit of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"children"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.27","order":"06.05.046.5891"},["b","27"],"And unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"bishop"],"of the church, and unto such as God shall appoint and ordain to watch over the church and to be elders unto the church, are to have it given unto them to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"discern"],"all those gifts lest there shall be any among you professing and yet be not of God."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.28","order":"06.05.046.5892"},["b","28"],"And it shall come to pass that he that asketh in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Spirit"],"shall receive in Spirit;"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.29","order":"06.05.046.5893"},["b","29"],"That unto some it may be given to have all those gifts, that there may be a head, in order that every member may be profited thereby."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.30","order":"06.05.046.5894"},["b","30"],"He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"asketh"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"Spirit"],"asketh according to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"will"],"of God; wherefore it is done even as he asketh."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.31","order":"06.05.046.5895"},["b","31"],"And again, I say unto you, all things must be done in the name of Christ, whatsoever you do in the Spirit;"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.32","order":"06.05.046.5896"},["b","32"],"And ye must give",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"thanks"],"unto God in the Spirit for whatsoever blessing ye are blessed with."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.33","order":"06.05.046.5897"},["b","33"],"And ye must practice",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"virtue"],"and holiness before me continually. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.1a","order":"06.05.046.5898"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/10.13.12-13"},"Deut. 10:13 (12–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.2a","order":"06.05.046.5900"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/9.1"},"Lev. 9:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1"},"Alma 6:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.2b","order":"06.05.046.5902"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9"},"Moro. 6:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.45"},"D&C 20:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.3a","order":"06.05.046.5904"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.22.22-34"},"3 Ne. 18:22 (22–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.3b","order":"06.05.046.5906"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church"},"TG Church"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fellowshipping"},"Fellowshipping"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meetings"},"Meetings"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.4a","order":"06.05.046.5908"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.24.23-26"},"3 Ne. 12:24 (23–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.4b","order":"06.05.046.5910"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrament"},"Sacrament"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.5a","order":"06.05.046.5912"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.6a","order":"06.05.046.5914"},["b","6a"],["span.small","IE"],"for confirmation of those recently baptized, commonly done now in sacrament meeting."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7a","order":"06.05.046.5916"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.5.5-6"},"James 1:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.11"},"D&C 6:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.62.62-65"},"88:62 (62–65)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/102.23"},"102:23"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/problem-solving"},"TG Problem-Solving"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7b","order":"06.05.046.5918"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7c","order":"06.05.046.5920"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meditation"},"TG Meditation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7d","order":"06.05.046.5922"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/34.1.1-3"},"Ps. 34:1 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.30.30-31"},"69:30 (30–31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.38"},"Alma 34:38"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"7e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7e","order":"06.05.046.5924"},["b","7e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/4.1.1-4"},"1 Tim. 4:1 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11"},"D&C 28:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.6.5-7"},"43:6 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7f","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7f","order":"06.05.046.5926"},["b","7f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"7g","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7g","order":"06.05.046.5928"},["b","7g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.22.18-22"},"Col. 2:22 (18–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/1.14"},"Titus 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.6.6-7"},"D&C 3:6 (6–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.29"},"45:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19"},"JS—H 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.8a","order":"06.05.046.5930"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.31"},"1 Cor. 12:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.10"},"D&C 11:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.9a","order":"06.05.046.5932"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sign-seekers"},"TG Sign Seekers"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.9b","order":"06.05.046.5934"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3"},"James 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.10a","o